column5: I finally registered after trolling for quite some time. Hopefully I can  help here and there. Kenny G
Welcome to the board! So why aren't you out fishing this morning?
A full bottle of red wine last. I have to go do laundry also. Thanks, Kenny G
Welcome to the board Kenny    Since you are doing laundry this morning, care to do mine so I can go fishing?  lol
Welcome!!!  Do you own a camera, and take pics of the fish you catch?  ... we love fish pics here!!!
Hey, welcome to OFC! as GCD said we love pictures and fishing reports. Are you a multi-species angler or is there a favored species that you like to target?   Best Regards,  Mike

Probably have a 8 loads to do and two kids to watch. Kinda have my hands full. Thanks for the offer though maybe the next time. Have a digital camera and love to snap. Going to Bracebridge next weekend for pike/walleye opener. Kenny G.
Welcome to OFC Kenny G You've made the right decision in joining the best site on the planet Looking forward to your future reports! Leechman
Welcome to the board. But you could have chosen a different name. All I can picture is the long haired horn blower...
Maybe he likes to blow his own horn?  Welcome
Oh,man. have you just done a grave-mistake.
Ya I know. Fish everything their Mike. Live right on the lake and rivers edge in Port Credit. Love where I live. Icefishing the Credit in the winter with Stevie for chrome. Kenny G.
